Songwe. Songwe Regional Commissioner Chiku Galawa (pictured) has urged business operators to engage themselves in a truly competitive business world so as to prosper.She gave the advice yesterday during the opening of a seminar to the region s traders on the importance of formalising their ventures. The five-day training is conducted by the Business Registration and Licensing Agency. Take advantage of this opportunity and change for the better, Ms Galawa said. She noted that the initiative was an opportunity for people in the region to change and stop doing things unprofessionally.